tourBios.carHigh: Earned non-exempt status with rounds of 70-73-73-70 at the 2013 Qualifying Tournament.

dyn.dynBios: Favorite golf course is Torrey Pines...Big fan of San Diego Chargers and Padres...Dream foursome would include Dad, Mom and Son Kai...Is involved with the Marshall Faulk Foundation...Runs a commercial fishing boat in the Cook Inlet, Alaska.
